---
title: Grilled Beef and Pork Patty Melts with Caramelized Onions and Dill Pickle Slaw
description: Patty melts cooked on the grill adds a delicious smokiness to these classic cheesy wonders. Spoon savoury-sweet caramelized onions over top for a next-level burger experience. Plates will be clean in no time!
